<sect1 id="dir_d87aa54b7978b1d43e58860ce289fb89_1autotoc_md222">
<title>helios::engine::runtime::spawn::behavior::placements</title><para>Concrete SpawnPlacer implementations.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_d87aa54b7978b1d43e58860ce289fb89_1autotoc_md223">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides ready-to-use SpawnPlacer implementations for determining spawn positions.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_d87aa54b7978b1d43e58860ce289fb89_1autotoc_md224">
<title>Key Classes</title><para><table rows="3" cols="2"><row>
